                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> If the pet is doing 100% damage ...meaning you do ZERO ...then your pet is taking the xp.  The pet xp changes from not too long ago simply made it where the pet wouldn't take half the xp for doing more than half the damage.  <br /><br />Now, so long as you do 1 point of damage, you get 100% of the experience.  If you do no damage ...ZERO ...then your pet takes -I believe- 100% of the experience (whereas before, he would have taken half).<br /><br />Clear as mud, eh?<br /><br /><center><img src="http://members.cox.net/eleceagle/images/rigorre4h.jpg" border=0></center></span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
